.TH GPASTE APPLET 1
.SH NAME
GPaste-Applet \- An applet for the GPaste clipboard manager

.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.B gpaste applet

.SH "APPLET USAGE"

.SS
.B left clic
Display the history, the first element is the one in the clipboard
.br
.TP
.B left clic on an item
Select the item
.br
.TP
.B right clic on an item
Delete the item
.br

.SS
.B right clic
Display the options
.br
.TP
.B Settings
Launch the configuration tool
.br
.TP
.B Empty history
Empty the history
.br
.TP
.B Quit
Exit the applet
.br

